              <li>• Social isolation due to schedule misalignment with friends and family</li>
              <li>• Relationship strain from incompatible schedules with partner</li>
              <li>• Guilt and shame about being a "night person" in a "day person's world"</li>
              <li>• Previous therapy attempts failed due to scheduling conflicts</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
