            Sofia was matched with <strong>Dr. Rachel Martinez</strong>, a licensed clinical psychologist who specialized in anxiety disorders and had personal experience as a night owl herself. Dr. Martinez offered appointments until midnight EST, which meant Sofia could have sessions at 9 or 10 PM Chicago time—perfect for her between getting up and heading to work.
          </p>

